Package org.aludratest.scheduler.sort

Class Summary
Alphabetic RunnerNode Comparator which evaluates the alphabetical order of the nodes' path names.
AlphabeticDescending RunnerNode Comparator which evaluates the alphabetical order of the nodes' path names in a descending manner.
BreadthFirst RunnerNode Comparator which puts test leafs to the head of the list.
DefaultNodeComparator Default Comparator for RunnerNodes which delegates to the Alphabetic comparator.
DepthFirst RunnerNode Comparator which puts test groups to the head of the list.
FallbackComparator Multi-Step RunnerNode Comparator which uses a list of RunnerNode Comparators.
NoComparator RunnerNode Comparator which is meant to indicate that no sorting should be applied.
ReverseNodeComparator RunnerNode Comparator inverts the order of another (base) Comparator.
RunnerTreeSorter Helper class for sorting Runner Trees with the help of a Comparator.
SequentialFirst RunnerNode Comparator which puts serial test groups to the head of the list.
